<p><span class="anchor" id="p50"></span>فِي الْأَصَح لَا مكَاتب فِي الْأَصَح أَو<a href="#p50" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p51"></span>حلف<a href="#p51" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
